|2 |  └─MERGE GROUP BY                |        |10000   |0           |
|3 |    └─EXCHANGE IN MERGE SORT DISTR|        |10000   |6267        |
|4 |      └─EXCHANGE OUT DISTR (HASH) |:EX10000|10000   |0           |
|5 |        └─PX PARTITION ITERATOR   |        |10000   |0           |
|6 |          └─MERGE GROUP BY        |        |10000   |0           |
|7 |            └─TABLE FULL SCAN     |A(i2)   |1000000 |0           |
======================================================================
